Here’s my latest Poem-Painting titled “Daddy’s Little Girl”. 

We always hear about how important it is for a Man to be in his Son’s Life but I’ve always felt it is just as equally important for a Father to be in his Daughter’s Life as well. So I created this piece to visually & poetically show how I felt about this precious bond…. #ArtByLegend 🎨👨🏽‍🍼🤍

In honor of “International Women’s Day” Here’s the custom portrait that I painted of some of the most Influential Black Women in Today’s World. It’s titled “A Black Girl’s Dream turned into a Black Woman’s Reality”.... I wanted to shine light on these powerful Black Women who have provided our young black girls with a vision that they can grow up & truly be whatever it is they desire to be but most importantly be able to one day break barriers & change the world.... 

The 5 Women in the portrait are as follows: Politician, Lawyer & Activist @staceyabrams . Forever our 1st Lady @michelleobama . The Mayor of Atlanta @keishabottoms . The 1st Black Female Vice President @kamalaharris & The U.S. Representative for California’s 43rd District @repmaxinewaters 

#ArtByLegend #BlackPower #BLM #BlackArt #PortraitArtist #ArtIsLife #BlackLivesMatter #BlackWomen 💯✊🏾🎨🏆🎤

“Transparency Post” Being a Teacher was never a Goal of mine but when God calls you to do something you can’t question it, You have to answer the Call. The Greatest Responsibility is to be expected to change someone else’s Life & Being a Teacher you’re expected to do that times 10!! Yes it’s a tough task but I wake up everyday & pray that I touch the young lives that God needs me to touch each day. If you ask my students they all are gunna say something along the lines of “Coach crazy but he Cool” lol But each of them know that I’m always there for them & The Love they showed me for Teacher Appreciation Week really let me know that I’m doing what God needed me to do. So to every student that I’ve ever taught & every player that I’ve ever coached I love y’all & Appreciate y’all for allowing me to make a difference in your lives…. 🙏🏽🥹🤍👨🏽‍🏫

#TeacherAppreciationWeek

To my Daughters @shaylaa.monaee & @_xoxokaayy We done been through it all this year “Mainly them taking turns stressing me out” But even if given the chance I wouldn’t change a thing cause it did nothing but make our bond that much stronger!! Know that I’m soo proud of y’all & Pops got y’all 4L!! 

To @_liyah2pr3tty._ & @bri_dabarbieeee Lord knows I’m glad I don’t have to fuss at y’all anymore lol But like always I’m gone be there whenever y’all need me!! 

To my lil sisters @caarsynnn & @the0nlymaddie.ee The main thing Ima miss is the laughs!! Y’all wouldn’t let me have a bad day even if I wanted to lol I’m forever proud of both of y’all!! 

Lastly my bruddas @tmd.don @1luhhted_ @_1luhzxy @luhjq__ Being able to Coach y’all this year was a Blessing But seeing y’all grow from Boys to Young Men is the Best blessing of all!! Y’all boys know we locked in 4L!!! 

Being a Teacher & Coach are the paths that God chose for me so I can touch other lives & Moments like these remind me to never forget that…. #Legend 🤞🏽💯🎓

With my 5th Solo Art Exhibit being only ✌🏽 days away I’ve spent the past few days just reflecting & appreciating how far I have come as an Artist. One quote that I always keep with me is, “The most beautiful thing is not the Finishline, It’s the Journey that you took to get there that matters the most”…. 

Here’s some pics from my first 4 Solo Art Exhibits ((2013, 2015, 2019 & 2022)) 🔥🎨🙏🏽💯

#ArtByLegend #LiveYourLegacy #LegendaryLetters

The Countdown is Real‼️We’re less than 24hrs away from my 5th Solo Art Exhibit titled “Legendary Letters”!! So here’s a sneak peek of the Lineup…. See y’all Tomorrow‼️ 

Location: @allure_events_center 
Time: 4-6pm 
Admission: $10 (Pay at the Door)

Today was truly a Day that I’ll keep in my Heart Forever‼️‼️God, I Thank You for blessing me with this Talent & The Ability to touch lives with it!! My 5th Solo Art Exhibit “Legendary Letters”was a Huge Success!!! 

I have to send a Huge “THANK YOU!!” To everyone that came out & enjoyed this experience with me Today‼️ To have a room once again filled with 150+ people that love Me & Support Me really means the World to me!! I Love Each & Every One of y’all‼️

The quote for Today “The Greatness of a Man is determined by his Ability to positively make a difference in those Lives around him” & I promise to continue to live by exactly this…. 🙏🏽💯✍🏽👨🏽‍🎨🔥🎨

#ArtByLegend #LiveYourLegacy #LegendaryLetters
Gotta Send a Huge Shoutout to @bridamvp for snapping these 🔥🔥 photos at my Art Exhibit yesterday‼️ Make sure y’all tap in with her for any Photo Needs!! 📸💯🔥🎨

Here’s a 2min Intro\Recap Video of my 5th Solo Art Show “Legendary Letters” that I had this past Saturday‼️ Shoutout to my Cameraman @victorrashad for always coming with the 🔥🔥 Visuals too!! And “Thank you 🙏🏽” to each & every one of you that came out to Support & Enjoy this Experience with me!! 

((P.S. My Speech Video will be dropping soon as well)) 
#ArtByLegend #LegendaryLetters 🔥🎨📸

This Speech is probably the most Powerful Speech I’ve ever given because it’s a conversation that I had with a room filled with people who Love & Support Me. A Moment where I could just be Honest & Genuine about this journey that I am taking with GOD & my Art. I hope those who are watching this listens with a Clear Mind & Open Heart so it can touch you like it did for everyone in the room that day. And with that being said here is my Artist Speech from my Art Exhibit “Legendary Letters”…. #ArtByLegend #LegendaryLetters 🙏🏽🥹❤️‍🔥🎨🎤

Special Shoutout to my Videographer @victorrashad for bringing my Vision to Life with the 🔥🔥🔥 everytime‼️

“What I want people to take away from my music is just how to take care of responsibilities. How to live life & enjoy life. You only get one shot at life, one life to live, Make the most out of it. Put as many smiles as you can on people’s faces. Help as many people as you can. Get you some paper. Live life, you and your folks”…. - Young Dolph

“APPRECIATION POST‼️” 4yrs ago on this date this precious girl gained her Angel Wings. Her mother @danas_mommy_08 reached out to me to create this painting afterwards & I immediately knew that I had to make this happen for her Family. Losing a loved one is never easy so I try to use my talent to provide some peace for my supporters when they need me. I haven’t painted in months but today reminded me that GOD still has work for me to do!! @danas_mommy_08 I’m forever Thankful for you choosing me to do the painting & Know that Dana’s spirit is still here!! #ArtByLegend 🙏🏽🤍🎨🕊️
